<section class="sf-register-context">
    <p class="sf-marketing-eyebrow">Business onboarding preview</p>
    <h1>Set up the tenant shell before the team ever enters `sms` or `mls`.</h1>
    <p class="sf-register-lead">
        This registration surface is the future entry point for MSMEs subscribing to ServiFinance.
        It frames the business, the owner account, and the plan mix before activation.
    </p>

    <div class="sf-register-steps">
        <article class="sf-register-step">
            <span>01</span>
            <div>
                <h2>Define the business identity</h2>
                <p>Reserve the business name and tenant-domain slug that will anchor the tenant-specific routes.</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="sf-register-step">
            <span>02</span>
            <div>
