    </div>

    <div class="sf-register-benefits">
        <div>
            <strong>SMS Web Workspace</strong>
            <span>Customer intake, service tracking, dispatching, and invoicing.</span>
        </div>
        <div>
            <strong>MLS Desktop Surface</strong>
            <span>Collections, schedules, and micro-lending operations under one tenant identity.</span>
        </div>
        <div>
            <strong>Root-Domain Oversight</strong>
            <span>Subscription and platform control stay separate from tenant execution.</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
